00:01:36.300 --> 00:01:37.460
using child adoptions as a front

00:01:37.460 --> 00:01:38.820
to cover up the opium trade.

00:01:40.020 --> 00:01:40.700
Right now,

00:01:41.460 --> 00:01:43.180
he's probably moving the goods
to the dock.

00:01:45.900 --> 00:01:46.700
Where are you going?

00:01:47.020 --> 00:01:47.900
I'm going to expose him.

00:01:48.300 --> 00:01:49.700
Wang Wan'er is already dead.

00:01:49.900 --> 00:01:51.100
Wang Penghui must have hidden

00:01:51.100 --> 00:01:52.500
all that evidence tightly.

00:01:52.780 --> 00:01:53.780
Going now?

00:01:54.100 --> 00:01:55.620
Isn't that just heading for your doom?

00:01:56.340 --> 00:01:57.140
Rumeng,

00:01:57.860 --> 00:01:59.060
I know you're filled with hatred.

00:01:59.260 --> 00:01:59.900
I said

00:01:59.900 --> 00:02:01.740
I've got your back, no matter what.

00:02:02.540 --> 00:02:03.900
But if you go like this now,

00:02:04.420 --> 00:02:05.660
think how much
it would break Hua's heart.

00:02:06.620 --> 00:02:07.340
She wouldn't want to see

00:02:07.340 --> 00:02:08.980
you die by Wang Penghui's hand.

00:02:11.780 --> 00:02:12.580
Meng,

00:02:13.180 --> 00:02:15.660
you can't live in the shadow
of the past forever.

00:02:17.980 --> 00:02:18.780
Promise me,

00:02:20.460 --> 00:02:21.780
if you're in danger,

00:02:22.980 --> 00:02:24.300
you must protect yourself.

00:02:26.220 --> 00:02:27.660
When all this is over,

00:02:29.100 --> 00:02:30.500
start a new life.

00:02:38.020 --> 00:02:39.340
Hua is dead too.

00:02:42.740 --> 00:02:45.500
I've lost everyone dear to me.

00:02:47.300 --> 00:02:49.260
Should I not have sought revenge?

00:02:49.740 --> 00:02:51.260
I have nothing left.

00:02:52.900 --> 00:02:54.660
I have nothing left!

00:02:57.740 --> 00:02:58.700
You still have me.

