Sir,

00:03:33.260 --> 00:03:35.300
we delivered the invitations
house-to-house.

00:03:40.980 --> 00:03:41.740
Sir,

00:03:42.260 --> 00:03:44.300
maybe they just don't want to come?

00:03:51.180 --> 00:03:54.260
Sir, he also sent word.

00:03:55.740 --> 00:03:57.100
He said if Liu Rumeng isn't dead,

00:03:57.220 --> 00:03:58.900
the cooperation ends here.

00:04:06.100 --> 00:04:07.540
Enough. You may go.

00:04:57.300 --> 00:04:58.380
- Congratulations, Mr. Wang,
- Congratulations, Mr. Wang,

