- on becoming Chamber President!
- on becoming Chamber President!

00:05:00.220 --> 00:05:00.940
Thank you, everyone!

00:05:00.940 --> 00:05:01.740
Thank you!

00:05:01.980 --> 00:05:03.900
From now on, we're all in the same boat!

00:05:04.460 --> 00:05:05.700
We'll share the blessings,

00:05:06.060 --> 00:05:07.500
and I'll take the hardships alone.

00:05:09.340 --> 00:05:09.860
Have a drink!

00:05:09.860 --> 00:05:10.740
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:05:10.820 --> 00:05:11.460
- Come on!
- Come on!

